Busting the myths of #BDD by @gojkoadzic. #1: Instoolation: Belief that process problems can be solved by installing a tool

Busting the myths of #BDD by @gojkoadzic #3: Acceptegration: Belief that tests are either unit or acceptance-integration
Busting the myths of #BDD by @gojkoadzic #4: Rolation: <insert role> should do BDD in isolation (eg testers do everything)
Busting the myths of #BDD by @gojkoadzic #5: Longression: Belief that the long term value of BDD is in regression testing
